    "A comprehensive overview of recent advances in vision transformers across backbone, high/mid-level vision, low-level vision, video processing, multimodality, and efficient transformer methods.",
    "A categorization of transformer models by application scenarios, including backbone network, high/mid-level vision, low-level vision, and video processing.",
